#Aesculus chinensis Bunge
Genus: Aesculus section: Calothyrsus
Family: Sapindaceae subfamily: Hippocastanoideae tribe: Hippocastaneae. Also placed in: Hippocastanaceae
Nomen number: 1625
Place of publication: Enum. pl. China bor. 10. 1833 (Mém. Acad. Imp. Sci. Saint-Pétersbourg Divers Savans 2:84. 1835)
Name verified on: 02-Jan-1995 by ARS Systematic Botanists. Last updated: 10-Nov-2010
Species priority site is: National Arboretum (NA).
Accessions: 2 in National Plant Germplasm System. 